dd5b06adb1db81bc6c24a746b6d9e554289c","Node name for S&R":"FilmAuteur_LTXV","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.8"},"groupState_grp_input_controls":false,"groupState_grp_ollama_enhance":false,"groupState_grp_timeline_controls":false,"groupState_grp_sampling":false,"groupState_grp_refinement":false,"groupState_grp_vram_optimization":false},"widgets_values":["Henry: A 35-year-old man with a rugged, chiseled jawline and short, neatly styled salt-and-pepper hair. He has deep-set hazel eyes, thick eyebrows, and a well-groomed, dense stubble beard. His skin features a slightly weathered, warm olive complexion. He possesses a tall, broad-shouldered, and subtly muscular build, dressed in a fitted, thick charcoal-grey wool turtleneck sweater paired with dark indigo denim jeans and worn brown leather boots. His expression is stoic and intensely focused, conveying a sense of quiet confidence, with his strong, slightly calloused hands resting casually by his sides.\nSamantha: A 25-year-old woman with a striking, angular face and vibrant ginger-red hair styled in a sleek, chin-length bob with sharp, blunt bangs. She has a pale, heavily freckled complexion and large, expressive emerald-green eyes framed by naturally long, dark lashes. She has a slender, athletic physique and wears a vibrant mustard-yellow silk long-sleeve blouse tucked into high-waisted, tailored black trousers secured by a thin black leather belt. She is accessorized with delicate gold hoop earrings and a minimalist gold pendant necklace. Her posture is perfectly upright and elegant, and she wears a subtle, warm smile that highlights her naturally high cheekbones.","Study: The set is a dimly lit, rustic study defined by deep mahogany paneled walls and a heavily distressed Persian rug in rich burgundies and faded golds spanning a dark hardwood floor. Anchoring the dead center of the room is a massive, scarred walnut trestle table, oriented parallel to the camera. Placed directly in the middle of the table’s surface lies an unrolled, intricately detailed parchment map, its curled corners pinned flat by a tarnished brass compass on the top left and a heavy crystal magnifying glass on the bottom right. A tufted leather armchair sits pushed back from the table at a sharp forty-five-degree angle toward stage right. Illumination is primarily provided by a single, focused beam of warm, golden hour sunlight slicing diagonally through a tall, mullioned window on the stage left wall, catching floating dust motes and illuminating the map's faded topography. Secondary, practical lighting comes from a green-glass banker's lamp stationed at the back right corner of the table, casting a localized pool of warm amber light and throwing deep, cinematic shadows across the floor-to-ceiling bookshelves that flank the background. Centered perfectly on the upstage wall, serving as the room's primary focal point and exit, is a heavy, arched oak door reinforced with thick, blackened wrought-iron hinges and an oversized, rustic iron lock plate.","Medium shot of Henry leaning over a wooden table, intensely studying a weathered map, his brow furrowed in concentration. | Over-the-shoulder shot as Samantha enters the frame, her vibrant mustard blouse catching the light, and confidently taps a specific location on the map. | Close-up on Henry as he shifts his gaze from the map to Samantha, his stoic expression softening as he asks, \"Are you sure this is the place?\" | Medium close-up of Samantha smiling warmly, her emerald eyes bright, as she holds up an ornate iron key and replies, \"I've never been more sure of anything.\" | Close-up on their hands as Henry's calloused fingers carefully take the key from Samantha, a subtle nod of quiet confidence passing between them. | Wide shot of Henry and Samantha turning away from the table, walking side-by-side toward a heavy oak door, projecting a sense of shared determination.","text-to-video","▼ Input",false,fa